data.description: This beautiful & cozy home is located in a quiet neighborhood. Immediately experience the welcome and warmth from home as you step inside its open foyer entrance that leads you straight to its elegant Family Room with fireplace. The large Dining room attractively stands out on the left. The lovely Kitchen includes its own Dining/ Breakfast area. Enjoy the unique location of 3 of the 4 bedrooms which are on the Lower level in this 2-story home. The large and spacious Master Bedroom is connected to its very own Full Bathroom with vanity, separate shower and a huge walk-in closet. As you travel down the long hallway you will find 2 inviting bedrooms conveniently located on your left with a Full Bathroom to be shared with the Bedroom on the right. The Laundry Room is conveniently located on the main level and guides you to the hallway upstairs to the 4th private and roomy spacious Bedroom. This home offers plenty of backyard space, patio and newly completed gorgeous DECK for all of your outside entertainment needs. APPOINTMENT ONLY - Contact Listing Agent: Felicia Ward at 678-218-7231.
